Company Profile
Sector: Communications
Industry: Media
Sub-Industry: Internet Media
Wikia, Inc. provides hosting services. The Company helps online communities discuss and share information in the areas of auto, books, creative, education, entertainment, finance, gaming, lifestyle, music, philosophy, politics, sports, technology, toys, and travel. Wikia serves users worldwide.




